column5: ~~~Well Brain what other then World dominates, where are you planning to Phish this weekend, Well Pinky, I'm planning on shortening the backyard grass again, on Saturday, then chase some Walleyes and catphish on Sunday. Sounds god wonder what the rest of the world is doing

Vacation started 2 hours ago  Walleye tournament tomorrow  A week of fishing carp, perch and walleye with my brother and buddy who are also on vacation  Wrapped up nicely with zone 18 musky Opener  Life is good
